Frequently Asked Question

Ask a Question

Here's what some of my satisfied clients have to say about my work

Ask a Question

How do you help us exactly?

We consult on your lead generation and management system, using data and experience to build a more efficient system, saving you time and improving conversion rates by pre-qualifying leads.

How will you know what to build for us?

Our process is simple and our discovery workshop allows us to deep dive into what's working and what's not working inside your sales process. Our team of experts will then build a timeline of deliverables and start implementing our systems into

How quickly will we see results?

Most clients will see both time saving results and improved lead quality within the first 14 days of having their new system live. This depends on the amount of leads being generated and the type of business you operate.

What platforms and channels can your chatbots integrate with?

COGNIFY's chatbot systems can integrate with a variety of platforms and channels, including websites, messaging apps, social media platforms, and more, ensuring flexibility and accessibility for your customers

How does COGNIFY ensure data privacy and security for our customers' interactions with the chatbots?

At COGNIFY, we prioritize data privacy and security. Our chatbot systems are built with robust encryption protocols and adhere to strict privacy standards to safeguard customer interactions and sensitive data, ensuring peace of mind for both businesses and their customers.
